{"id":746,"parent_id":702,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":746,"title":"Isaiah 44","subtitle":"","short_title":"Isa.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 44"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord’s Spirit will be poured out on the descendants of Israel—Idols of wood are as fuel for a fire—The Lord will gather, bless, and redeem Israel and rebuild Jerusalem."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.1","order":"02.24.044.48499"},["b","1"],"Yet now hear, O Jacob my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"servant"],"; and Israel, whom I have chosen:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.2","order":"02.24.044.48500"},["b","2"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"that made thee, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"formed"],"thee from the womb,",["i","which"],"will help thee; Fear not, O Jacob, my servant; and thou,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"Jesurun"],", whom I have chosen."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.3","order":"02.24.044.48501"},["b","3"],"For I will pour water upon",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"him"],"that is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"thirsty"],", and floods upon the dry ground: I will pour my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"spirit"],"upon thy seed, and my blessing upon thine offspring:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.4","order":"02.24.044.48502"},["b","4"],"And they shall spring up",["i","as"],"among the grass, as willows by the water courses."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.5","order":"02.24.044.48503"},["b","5"],"One shall say, I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Lord"]],"’s; and another shall call",["i","himself"],"by the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"name"],"of Jacob; and another shall subscribe",["i","with"],"his hand unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and surname",["i","himself"],"by the name of Israel."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.6","order":"02.24.044.48504"},["b","6"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"King"],"of Israel, and his redeemer the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts; I",["i","am"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"first"],", and I",["i","am"],"the last; and beside me",["i","there is"],"no God."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.7","order":"02.24.044.48505"},["b","7"],"And who, as I, shall call, and shall declare it, and set it in order for me, since I appointed the ancient people? and the things that are coming, and shall come, let them shew unto them."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.8","order":"02.24.044.48506"},["b","8"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Fear"],"ye not, neither be afraid: have not I told thee from that time, and have declared",["i","it?"],"ye",["i","are"],"even my witnesses. Is there a God beside me? yea,",["i","there is"],"no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"God"],"; I know not",["i","any."]],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.9","order":"02.24.044.48507"},["b","9"],"¶They that make a graven",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"image"],["i","are"],"all of them vanity; and their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"delectable things"],"shall not profit; and they",["i","are"],"their own witnesses; they",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"see not"],", nor know; that they may be ashamed."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.10","order":"02.24.044.48508"},["b","10"],"Who hath formed a god, or molten a graven",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"image"],["i","that"],"is profitable for nothing?"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.11","order":"02.24.044.48509"},["b","11"],"Behold, all his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"fellows"],"shall be ashamed: and the workmen, they",["i","are"],"of men: let them all be gathered together, let them stand up;",["i","yet"],"they shall fear,",["i","and"],"they shall be ashamed together."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.12","order":"02.24.044.48510"},["b","12"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"smith"],"with the tongs both worketh in the coals, and fashioneth it with hammers, and worketh it with the strength of his arms: yea, he is hungry, and his strength faileth: he drinketh no water, and is faint."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.13","order":"02.24.044.48511"},["b","13"],"The carpenter stretcheth out",["i","his"],"rule; he marketh it out with a line; he fitteth it with planes, and he marketh it out with the compass, and maketh it after the figure of a man, according to the beauty of a man; that it may remain in the house."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.14","order":"02.24.044.48512"},["b","14"],"He heweth him down cedars, and taketh the cypress and the oak, which he strengtheneth for himself among the trees of the forest: he planteth an ash, and the rain doth nourish",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.15","order":"02.24.044.48513"},["b","15"],"Then shall it be for a man to burn: for he will take thereof, and warm himself; yea, he kindleth",["i","it,"],"and baketh bread; yea, he maketh a god, and worshippeth",["i","it;"],"he maketh it a graven image, and falleth down thereto."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.16","order":"02.24.044.48514"},["b","16"],"He burneth part thereof in the fire; with part thereof he eateth flesh; he roasteth roast, and is satisfied: yea, he warmeth",["i","himself,"],"and saith, Aha, I am warm, I have seen the fire:"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.17","order":"02.24.044.48515"},["b","17"],"And the residue thereof he maketh a god,",["i","even"],"his graven image: he falleth down unto it, and worshippeth",["i","it,"],"and prayeth unto it, and saith, Deliver me; for thou",["i","art"],"my god."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.18","order":"02.24.044.48516"},["b","18"],"They have not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"known"],"nor understood: for he hath",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"shut"],"their eyes, that they cannot see;",["i","and"],"their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"hearts"],", that they cannot understand."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.19","order":"02.24.044.48517"},["b","19"],"And none considereth in his heart, neither",["i","is there"],"knowledge nor understanding to say, I have burned part of it in the fire; yea, also I have baked bread upon the coals thereof; I have roasted flesh, and eaten",["i","it:"],"and shall I make the residue thereof an abomination? shall I fall down to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"stock"],"of a tree?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.20","order":"02.24.044.48518"},["b","20"],"He feedeth on ashes: a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"deceived"],"heart hath turned him aside, that he cannot deliver his soul, nor say,",["i","Is there"],"not a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"lie"],"in my right hand?"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.21","order":"02.24.044.48519"},["b","21"],"¶Remember",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"these"],", O Jacob and Israel; for thou",["i","art"],"my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"servant"],": I have formed thee; thou",["i","art"],"my servant: O Israel, thou shalt not be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"forgotten"],"of me."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.22","order":"02.24.044.48520"},["b","22"],"I have blotted out, as a thick cloud, thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"transgressions"],", and, as a cloud, thy sins: return unto me; for I have redeemed thee."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.23","order":"02.24.044.48521"},["b","23"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"Sing"],", O ye heavens; for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath done",["i","it:"],"shout, ye lower parts of the earth: break forth into",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"singing"],", ye mountains, O forest, and every tree therein: for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"redeemed"],"Jacob, and glorified himself in Israel."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.24","order":"02.24.044.48522"},["b","24"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"redeemer"],", and he that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"formed"],"thee from the womb, I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"that",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_24c"},"maketh"],"all",["i","things;"],"that stretcheth forth the heavens alone; that spreadeth abroad the earth by myself;"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.25","order":"02.24.044.48523"},["b","25"],"That frustrateth the tokens of the liars, and maketh diviners mad; that turneth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"wise"],["i","men"],"backward, and maketh their knowledge foolish;"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.26","order":"02.24.044.48524"},["b","26"],"That confirmeth the word of his servant, and performeth the counsel of his messengers; that saith to Jerusalem, Thou shalt be inhabited; and to the cities of Judah, Ye shall be built, and I will raise up the decayed places thereof:"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.27","order":"02.24.044.48525"},["b","27"],"That saith to the deep, Be dry, and I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"dry up"],"thy rivers:"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.28","order":"02.24.044.48526"},["b","28"],"That saith of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"Cyrus"],",",["i","He is"],"my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"shepherd"],", and shall perform all my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_28c"},"pleasure"],": even saying to Jerusalem, Thou shalt be",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_28d"},"built"],"; and to the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_28e"},"temple"],", Thy foundation shall be laid."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.1a","order":"02.24.044.48527"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.21"},"Isa. 44:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/45.4"},"45:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.20"},"1 Ne. 20:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.2a","order":"02.24.044.48529"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/49.5"},"Isa. 49:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/1.5"},"Jer. 1:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.2b","order":"02.24.044.48531"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/33.26"},"Deut. 33:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.3a","order":"02.24.044.48533"},["b","3a"],["span.small","OR"],"that which is thirsty."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.3b","order":"02.24.044.48535"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.50.50-51"},"2 Ne. 9:50 (50–51)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.3c","order":"02.24.044.48537"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/36.27.26-27"},"Ezek. 36:27 (26–27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/2.17"},"Acts 2:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.5a","order":"02.24.044.48539"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conversion"},"TG Conversion"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-mission-of"},"Israel, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.5b","order":"02.24.044.48541"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.10.9-10"},"Abr. 2:10 (9–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.6a","order":"02.24.044.48543"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/kingdom-of-god-in-heaven"},"TG Kingdom of God, in Heaven"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.6b","order":"02.24.044.48545"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-jehovah"},"TG Jesus Christ, Jehovah"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.8a","order":"02.24.044.48547"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/41.10"},"Isa. 41:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.8b","order":"02.24.044.48549"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/45.5.5-22"},"Isa. 45:5 (5–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/46.9"},"46:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/6.7"},"2 Ne. 6:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/24.6"},"3 Ne. 24:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/1.6"},"Moses 1:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.9a","order":"02.24.044.48551"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/41.29.24,29"},"Isa. 41:29 (24, 29)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/21.17.17-19"},"3 Ne. 21:17 (17–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.16"},"D&C 1:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.9b","order":"02.24.044.48553"},["b","9b"],["span.small","HEB"],"beloved things; i.e., their idols."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.9c","order":"02.24.044.48555"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/115.5.5,8"},"Ps. 115:5 (5, 8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.10a","order":"02.24.044.48557"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.18"},"Hab. 2:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.11a","order":"02.24.044.48559"},["b","11a"],["span.small","IE"],"the fellow-worshippers of idols."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.12a","order":"02.24.044.48561"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/40.19.19-20"},"Isa. 40:19 (19–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.3.3-5"},"Jer. 10:3 (3–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.18a","order":"02.24.044.48563"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/45.20"},"Isa. 45:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.18b","order":"02.24.044.48565"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/4.14"},"Jacob 4:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.18c","order":"02.24.044.48567"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/19.33"},"3 Ne. 19:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.19a","order":"02.24.044.48569"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/superstitions"},"TG Superstitions"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.20a","order":"02.24.044.48571"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.12"},"Hosea 4:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/1.21"},"Rom. 1:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.20b","order":"02.24.044.48573"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/144.8"},"Ps. 144:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.21a","order":"02.24.044.48575"},["b","21a"],["span.small","IE"],"these things."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.21b","order":"02.24.044.48577"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.1.1-2"},"Isa. 44:1 (1–2)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/45.4"},"45:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.20"},"1 Ne. 20:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.21c","order":"02.24.044.48579"},["b","21c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/16.11.10-12"},"3 Ne. 16:11 (10–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/20.29.28-31"},"20:29 (28–31)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.22a","order":"02.24.044.48581"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/transgress"},"TG Transgress"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.23a","order":"02.24.044.48583"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/49.13"},"Isa. 49:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.23b","order":"02.24.044.48585"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/singing"},"TG Singing"],"."],["div",{"id":"23c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.23c","order":"02.24.044.48587"},["b","23c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-restoration-of"},"TG Israel, Restoration of"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.24a","order":"02.24.044.48589"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-jehovah"},"TG Jesus Christ, Jehovah"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.24b","order":"02.24.044.48591"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.5"},"1 Ne. 21:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"24c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.24c","order":"02.24.044.48593"},["b","24c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-creator"},"TG Jesus Christ, Creator"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.25a","order":"02.24.044.48595"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/1.20"},"1 Cor. 1:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.58"},"D&C 133:58"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.27a","order":"02.24.044.48597"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/50.38"},"Jer. 50:38"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/51.36"},"51:36"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.28a","order":"02.24.044.48599"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/governments"},"TG Governments"],"."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.28b","order":"02.24.044.48601"},["b","28b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/50.44"},"Jer. 50:44"],"."],["div",{"id":"28c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.28c","order":"02.24.044.48603"},["b","28c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/46.10"},"Isa. 46:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"28d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.28d","order":"02.24.044.48605"},["b","28d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/45.13"},"Isa. 45:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"28e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.28e","order":"02.24.044.48607"},["b","28e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/36.23.22-23"},"2 Chr. 36:23 (22–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/1.2.1-3"},"Ezra 1:2 (1–3)"],"."]]}
